[[File:Boxers Brief 1.jpg|thumb|'''Pants''' (England, Scotland)]]

# {{US|Canada|Australia|Ireland|Liverpool|plurale tantum}}  An outer [[garment]] worn by men and women that covers the body from the [[waist]] downwards, covering each leg separately, usually as far as the [[ankle]]s; [[trousers]].
# {{context|England|Scotland|plurale tantum}} An [[undergarment]] worn by men or women that covers the [[genitals]] and often the [[buttocks]] and the neighbouring parts of the body; [[underpants]], [[knickers]], [[panties]], [[shorts]].

